com.skratchdot.electribe.model.esx

Interface SongEventControl

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SongEvent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SongEventControlImpl

    public interface SongEventControl
extends SongEvent
    A representation of the model object 'Song Event Control'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Operation Type
    • Reserved Byte
    • Reserved Short
    • Value

    See Also:
    EsxPackage.getSongEventControl()
